* 1987½–1988 3.0&nbsp;L [[Mitsubishi 6G7x engine#6G72|Mitsubishi ''6G72'']] [[V6 engine|V6]], {{convert|136|hp|kW|abbr=on}}, {{convert|168|lbft|N.m|abbr=on}}
