| platform = [[Chrysler S platform|Chrysler RS platform]]
| engine = 2.4 L ''[[Chrysler Neon engine#2.4 and 2.4 Turbo|EDZ]]'' [[Straight-4|I4]]<br />2.8 L CRD [[Diesel fuel|diesel]] (Philippines)<br />3.0 L ''[[Mitsubishi 6G7 engine|6G72]] [[V6 engine|V6]]'' (China)<br />3.3 L ''[[Chrysler 3.3 engine#3.3|EGA]]'' [[V6 engine|V6]]<br />3.8 L ''[[Chrysler 3.3 engine#3.8|EGH]]'' V6
