{{Coord|47|11|N|23|3|E|display=title}} {{Infobox news event | title = 2007 Zalău explosion | date = {{start date|2007|9|14}} | time = 7:30 EEST (4:30 UTC) | image = {{Location map | Romania |float = center |caption = |label = Zalău |lat_deg = 47 |lat_min = 11 |lat_dir = N |lon_deg = 23 |lon_min = 3 |lon_dir = E}} | caption = Location of Zalău within Romania | place = [[Zalău]], [[Sălaj County]], [[Romania]] | reported injuries = 15 | reported death(s) = 2 }}
The '''Zalău explosion''' occurred on September 14, 2007 in a block of flats in [[Zalău]], [[Romania]] as the result of a [[gas leak]]. Two people died and eight were injured in the explosion.<ref>[[România Liberă]], [http://www.romanialibera.ro/actualitate/eveniment/explozie-devastatoare-la-zalau-2-morti-15-raniti-106076.html Explozie devastatoare la Zalau: 2 morti, 15 raniti]</ref> The structure was severely affected and the block of flats E24 was demolished in October 2007.<ref>[http://www.realitatea.net/blocul-din-zalau-avariat-de-explozie-este-demolat-astazi_95306.html Blocul din Zalău avariat de explozie este demolat astăzi]</ref> A total of 19 families were affected by the deflagration. They had been petitioning local natural gas distributor [[E.ON Gaz Romania|E.ON Gaz]] for two years before the explosion as a strong smell of gas could be sensed both inside and outside the block of flats.<ref>[http://hisz.rsoe.hu/alertmap/site/?pageid=event_desc&edis_id=EX-20070915-13387-ROU Explosion in Romania on Saturday, 15 September, 2007]</ref> The gas network system had been eight years overdue before the explosion.<ref>[http://www.evz.ro/detalii/stiri/ca-in-zalau-2007-explozia-din-sighet-crima-cu-premeditare-967580.html NEGLIJENŢĂ CRIMINALĂ. Zalău, 2007 - Sighet, 2012: două explozii identice. Putem sări în aer oricând]</ref>
On September 19, 2007, hundreds of people participated in the funeral of those who died in the explosion.<ref>[http://www.realitatea.net/cele-doua-victime-ale-exploziei-din-zalau-au-fost-inmormantate_90296.html Cele două victime ale exploziei din Zalău au fost înmormântate]</ref> Because E.ON Gaz did not provide support to the affected families, they protested in front of the headquarters of the company in [[Târgu Mureș]] on September 14, 2009.<ref>[http://www.realitatea.net/locatarii-blocului-din-zalau-distrus-de-o-explozie-in-2007-au-protestat-la-sediul-e-on-din-tg-mures_614202.html Locatarii blocului din Zalău distrus de o explozie în 2007 au protestat la sediul E.ON din Tg. Mureş]</ref><ref>[http://stirileprotv.ro/stiri/eveniment/protest-dupa-doi-ani-de-la-explozia-unui-bloc-din-zalau.html Protest dupa doi ani de la explozia unui bloc din Zalau!]</ref> In December 2010, six persons were sentenced to prison in connection with the explosion,<ref>[http://stirileprotv.ro/stiri/eveniment/sase-persoane-condamnate-in-cazul-unui-bloc-care-a-explodat-in-zalau.html Sase persoane condamnate in cazul unui bloc care a explodat in Zalau]</ref> but in December 2011 their sentences were suspended. Compensations owed to individuals ranged from 67,000 to 222,000 [[Romanian leu|lei]].<ref>[http://www.adevarul.ro/locale/zalau/Supravietuitorii_exploziei_blocului_E_24_loviti_din_nou-_nimeni_nu_face_puscarie_pentru_mortii_lor-iar_despagubirile_reduse_drastic_0_602339802.html Supravieţuitorii exploziei blocului E 24 loviţi din nou: nimeni nu face puşcărie pentru morţii lor, iar despăgubirile au fost reduse drastic]</ref> In March 2012, the former owners started to rebuild the block of flats.<ref>[http://www.graiulsalajului.ro/index.php?cmd=articol&idart=28094 Blocul E24 este reconstruit]</ref>
